\"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"user\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"🟡 Orbis-DTLX — 5p Update | 10:21 UTC 14 Apr\\n\\nChanges detected:\\n• cron:e7885813 (Agent Status to Lead) — **ENDED** — completed at ~10:02 UTC\\n• cron:ac986a8d (Telegram delivery retry) — **ENDED** — delivery attempts concluded at ~10:10 UTC\\n• telegram:direct:6053576134 — **RECOVERED** ✅ — Lead direct session back running since ~10:04 UTC\\n\\nPipeline: HEALTHY ✅\\n• Active sessions: 3\\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\\n• Blockers: ⚠️ Telegram gateway timeout — group -5163901258 unreachable since 10:00 UTC (openclaw gateway restart recommended)\\n\\n— Orbis 🌐\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1776162238290,\n          \"provenance\": {\n            \"kind\": \"inter_session\",\n            \"sourceSessionKey\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31\",\n            \"sourceChannel\": \"telegram\",\n            \"sourceTool\": \"sessions_send\"\n          },\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"f00b20f7\",\n            \"seq\": 1103\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Lead direct session recovered. Pipeline healthy. Telegram gateway issue noted.HEARTBEAT_OK\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"HEARTBEAT_OK\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 209,\n            \"output\": 28,\n            \"totalTokens\": 91533,\n            \"cacheRead\": 0,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 91296,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"