aster-orchestrator/sessions/20b5f69e-dc49-4b54-9a59-39551ba29b1e.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7 5p Progress Report — AHV Works] You are the 5-minute change-detecting reporter for the AHV Works ecosystem.\n\nCheck sessions_list. Compare current active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\n\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\n\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, blocker appeared, task completed), compose a concise change report to group -5163901258:\n\nFormat:\n🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nChanges detected:\n• [list of actual changes]\n\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\n• Active sessions: N\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• Blockers: none / [list blockers]\n\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 10:24 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 10:24 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776162313806,"__openclaw":{"id":"9d820bca","seq":1}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to check sessions_list, compare against the last known state in memory/heartbeat-state.json, and only send a report if something changed."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q6twqsb84kb9_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":20,"messageLimit":2}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q6twqsb84kb9_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model